# Arquitetura proposta

```
                   +----------------------+
                   |  Execution Graph     |
                   +----------+-----------+
                              |
                    executa próximo nó
                              |
                              ▼
                    +------------------+
                    | SkillNode        |
                    +------------------+
                              |
                     identifica ROLE
                              |
                              ▼
                 +--------------------------+
                 | Model Selection Layer    |
                 +--------------------------+
                  │                    │
          ROLE_LOCAL             ROLE_CRITIC
                  │                    │
